title: 78. If you have object versioning enabled on a multi-regional bucket, what will the following lifecycle config file do?
alternatives: A. Archive objects older than 30 days (the second rule doesn’t do anything)
B. Delete objects older than 30 days (the second rule doesn’t do anything)
